{"tid":1241858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】「反送中」運動凸顯「民主赤字」問題 英國籲香港進行民主改革","createTime":"2019-06-19T00:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T01:27:36.000Z","uid":70063,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"08c5f4aa5e6684bce4560cab2fd40eeaaea902ec","tid":1241858,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:41:24.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂引起的爭議沒有因為香港特首林鄭月娥周二公開道歉而結束，英國下議院周二再有議員就香港情況提出緊急質詢，政府官員和議員都認為香港須進行民主改革，糾正「民主赤字」（Democratic Deficit，指政府表現與民眾期望出現落差）問題。<br />\n<br />\n保守黨議員布魯斯（Fiona Bruce）問香港連番出現逾百萬人大遊行，是否代表關注焦點已擴展至過去幾年日益擴大的香港「民主赤字」，而港府應否展開民主改革，避免類似事件重演。<br />\n<br />\n外交部亞太事務國務大臣田銘祺（Mark Field）回應時，認同「民主赤字」令港人只能靠上街爭取訴求，建議香港考慮進行民主改革。<br />\n<br />\n下議院議長白高漢（John Bercow）對香港情況感到震驚與憤慨，對「反送中」示威者遭不合理對待提出譴責。<br />\n<br />\n自由民主黨國會議員卡邁克爾（Alistair Carmichael）和工黨女議員古德曼（Helen Goodman）都呼籲港府全面撤回修訂案。<br />\n<br />\n今次是下議院七天內第四度辯論香港情況，上而議院上周亦三度討論香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n另外，末代港督彭定康周二投書《泰晤士報》，呼籲英國政府應表明立場，要求香港政府撤回而非暫緩《逃犯條例修訂案》，指修訂案會拆毀香港與中國法治之間的防火牆。<br />\n<br />\n彭定康又認為，應就港警處理「反送中」示威的手法進行全面而公開的調查，調查應由獨立而德高望重的港人主持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190619/59732948?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190619%2F59732948%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8DFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=99e36cee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190619%2F59732948%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=cf7dc446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190619/59732948?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"512ce2354b58eb55028481a2e6e249b1dca6027a","tid":1241858,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">621我覺得可以同民陣討論<br />\n絕對唔係要比大台騎劫<br />\n但要明白民陣既一個呼籲比我地係連登開posts既聲音可以傳得更廣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"38c9256cc6944988710eadf535b32a1edb903efe","tid":1241858,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2873312fa8d3ac2a8f502d81a510fd6a5a011f9","tid":1241858,"uid":231523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:46:04.000Z","msg":"打少啲飛機啦，英國咪喺度講廢話"},{"pid":"c207bf8c1c2b1001bff7acc782c3d5d9d70419eb","tid":1241858,"uid":261530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:48:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"149a74d7483776dabe918ad12d213b08841cd177","tid":1241858,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}